title: La Revuelta
description: Darwin siente pena por los objetos del hogar en Elmore y los motiva a alzarse.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Fog
description: Victor and Valentino are fed up with Tez. He seems determined to ruin their summer in Monte Macabre. They see no other choice but to leave town for good. But will Tez let them?

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: La Suciedad
description: A Ben le encargan la tarea de limpiar la Chatarra, pero cuando, engañado por los viles villanos Fly Guys, permite que se lo roben, debe perseguirlos antes de que fabriquen una larva monstruosa imparable con un objetivo claro: destruir Las Vegas.

title: Be Afraid of the Dark
description: Ben travels into space to thwart Ghostfreak's diabolical plans. But is he hero enough to take on the Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein?

title: Makes Cookies/Not Afraid Anymore/Hates Vegetables/All Alone/Tidies His Toys
description: Caillou is having fun being noisy./Caillou is afraid of Mr. Hinkle, the kind neighbor./Caillou really hates vegetables./Mom is very busy with chores and doesn't have time to play with Caillou./Caillou has left his toys all over the place.

title: Drawn to Sports with Zachary
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Zachary loves competing and developing his skills in karate.

title: Revenge of the Swamp Monster!
description: Scooby-Doo and the Mystery Inc. gang meet up with basketball legend and bowling aficionado Chris Paul at a golf tournament fundraiser held in Florida. Shaggy's come to caddy for Mr. Paul and help him with this game so the Assist King can save a local school from going under. But, when a horrible Swamp Monster attacks trying to destroy the charity event, our heroes and Mr. Paul must finish the tournament and save the school, and possibly their own lives!

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Cuentos de miedo 2
description: Es Halloween de nuevo y la banda trata de contar aterradoras historias a un grupo de niños que piden dulces.

title: The Secret of the Ghost Rig
description: A mysterious ghost trucker is terrorizing Crystal Cove. Add to that all the doorknobs have begun to disappear from around town, someone has hidden a priceless diamond and Fred's dad, the Mayor, is up for re-election against a guy named Avocados. Scooby and the gang have their hands full. Oh, and did we mention Daphne has been set-up on a blind date with a pinhead named Rung Ladderton, who - wait for it - sells ladders for a living.

title: Historias de miedo
description: Durante la fiesta de Halloween de la banda, iUnikitty descubre que Rick no le teme a nada! Para contagiarle el espíritu festivo, Unikitty cuenta sus propias ideas de lo que es una historia espeluznante, con la esperanza de asustar al inconmovible de Rick por una vez. iPero cada cuento es aún más espeluznante (y más tonto) que el anterior!

title: #AmigasDelAlma Parte 1
description: En este episodio especial de dos partes, las chicas deben rastrear a Katana, una guerrera misteriosa que está robando las almas de los villanos de Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Tatsu, la nueva amiga de Diana, es su alma gemela en todo sentido, ipero puede que tenga una conexión con Katana!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Uncle Grandpa Sitter
description: Gus and Pizza Steve have plans to go out for the night, but UG can't be left alone in the RV, so they need a babysitter.  But when none are available, they turn to UG to babysit himself.

title: Clown College
description: While tailgating at a State U. homecoming football game, Ben teams up with Grandpa Max's old college buddies to keep the crazy clown Zombozo from robbing the stadium blind at halftime.

title: Kelsey la merecedora
description: Cuando Kelsey demuele una pared de la casa de Craig, su padre le quita la espada. Por eso, Kelsey les pide ayuda a Craig y a JP para que le demuestren a su padre que aún la merece.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Search Engine
description: On a mission to recover a pair of fuzzy dice from the junkyard, Tig and Seek battle it out with Boss' brand-new robot, Search Engine, to prove they're the better finders.

title: Horror Club
description: Steven goes to the lighthouse to watch scary movies with Ronaldo, Lars and Sadie.

title: Haunted RV
description: After Uncle Grandpa's Haunted House spirals out of control, the gang must save the teenagers stuck inside.

title: The Scratch Pack
description: Axel and the team must run damage control after a loose spark of Minergy accidentally turns Zoe's old toys - a set of cute squishy kittens - into a pack of snarling beasts.

title: Polly Ethylene and Tara Phthalate
description: Teen Titans Go takes a comedic look at the superheroes' lives. Viewers finally get the opportunity to watch what life is like for the super teens when their capes are left at home. The teens will deal with everyday issues of adolescence including laundry contests and quests to construct the perfect sandwich.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: The Vampire Strikes Back
description: Ben, Rook, and Rad Dudesman come face to face with the evil Lord Transyl, a vampire-like alien who can make anyone his loyal slave! (Introducing new Ben alien, Whampire.)

title: Concurso de Disfraces
description: Hartos de que los Hive Five les ganen en el concurso de disfraces, los Titanes elaboran un plan para ganar.

title: Cool Uncles
description: The Titans take a trip to Wackadoodles, but Trigon makes Raven babysit her little brothers.

title: Sarge esta a Cargo
description: Axel y el equipo deben rescatar a Sarge Charge de una misión en solitario en el patio trasero, que Orangutank ha convertido en su propio corazón personal de oscuridad.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: The Revolt
description: Darwin tries to highlight the plight of all the household objects he feels are being oppressed and maltreated by the uncaring residents of Elmore. He then decides to lead those objects in a revolt against the townspeople.

title: Sarge in Charge
description: Axel and the team must rescue Sarge Charge from a solo mission in the backyard, which Orangutank has turned into his own personal heart of darkness.

title: Tiggy Two-Shoes
description: Tiggy acts out to prove he can be a bad boy.

title: Fiesta en el Calabozo
description: Cole, Wu y la Princesa Vania conocen a un grupo de sobrevivientes llamados los de abajo, ellos cuentan cómo terminaron en "Lo más profundo".

title: La Espada Perdida
description: A León-O le recuerdan que debe conectar la Espada del Augurio al Cubil Felino todas las noches o la base se quedará sin energía. No hay problema, no es que León-O vaya a perder accidentalmente la espada o algo así, ¿verdad?

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Avistamiento de Ballenas
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan unirse a un club exclusivo para ver una ballena fuera de lo común.

title: Daycare/Joins the Circus/Afraid of the Dark/Friends/Visits the Doctor
description: It's Caillou's first day at daycare and he doesn't want to go./Caillou gets dressed all by himself./Caillou can't get to sleep./Caillou is talking to Grandma. She's surprised./Caillou has an ear infection.

title: The Eater
description: It's Halloween and Apple's not feeling quite right. He takes Onion into the dark depths to find out why.

title: El Corazon
description: El señor Robinson intenta recuperar la amistad de Gumball y Darwin y falla una y otra vez.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Fool Moon
description: Strange things start happening when Uncle Grandpa installs a moon roof in the RV.

title: #Powerless
description: Supergirl loses her powers and, with the help of BumbleBee, must rely on her street smarts to save Garth from vengeful Toyman.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Queen of the Munce
description: Jay, Nya and Lloyd are led deep into the Mines of Shintaro by Murt, who brings them back to the Munce "Home- Cave" - a settlement deep in the mountain. There, complications arise when they meet the Munce Queen, Murtessa, who takes a liking to Jay.

title: Monster Squad!
description: The Titans want to be the scariest trick-or-treaters in town, so Raven casts a spell to turn them into real monsters.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: All Paws on Deck
description: The gang climb aboard the cruise ship run by Fred's cousin, despite Velma's strong dislike of water. But a water phobia is the least of their problems when a terrifying sea monster attacks the ship!

title: Gyranoide del Futuro
description: Manzana y Cebollín se esfuerzan por subir a la montaña rusa más loca del parque de diversiones.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Villains' Night Out
description: Lord Boxman forces his way into an exclusive Villains party.

title: Elementary, My Dear Shaggy!
description: When Scooby and the gang are taking a tour of merry old London, they run afoul of horrible screaming skulls of English legend! They team up with an eccentric man who claims to be none other than Sherlock Holmes. Of course, he can't be the real thing, can he?

title: A Secret Tweet
description: The babies plan a surprise birthday party for Tweety.

title: Mystery Dungeon
description: Ice King, NEPTR, Tree Trunks, Shelby and Lemongrab are trapped inside a mysterious dungeon and must work together to free themselves.

title: The Haunted Dollhouse
description: Craig and his friends find themselves being followed by a creepy doll and its haunted dollhouse.

title: Happy Birthday Nancy
description: Seth wants his mom to have the best birthday ever, so he creates his own currency in order to buy her an expensive gift. But he learns a little too late that counterfeiting is a crime, putting Nancy's birthday at risk of being ruined.

title: Costume Crisis
description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

title: The Skull Sorcerer
description: Separated from the others, Cole must trust his instincts and make the right choices to find his way to the surface to alert King Vangelis of the dangerous Skull Sorcerer.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: A Clue for Scooby-Doo
description: Scooby and the gang become mixed up in a mystery when he surfs into what appears to be the ghost of Captain Cutler.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Save the Fun Tree
description: Mush-Mush and friends' favorite play tree, the Fun Tree, is rotten and doomed. But Mush-Mush refuses to give up on it. In a last ditch effort to save the tree, our friends adventure off to try and track down the legendary Starmush, hoping his mysterious healing powers can save it.

title: Mushroom Menace
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

title: Fideito
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben seguir teniendo la onda suficiente para aparecer en el video musical de su rapero favorito.

title: Mystery 101
description: Velma's got an interview at the prestigious Kingston University, the most selective school in the country. The only catch? The dean wants her and the rest of the Scooby gang to figure out why the ghost of Elias Kingston, the school's founder, is haunting Kingston's book-filled halls!

title: A Hole Lot of Trouble
description: When rain derails an outside game of catch someone suggests they play it inside. This prompts Izzy to lead the group through her wildly imaginative worst case scenario. It's an adventure so scary that the kids many never play again.

title: Nocaut
description: Axel y el equipo hacen malabarismos sin despertar al tío Andrew de su siesta y evitar que Orangutank robe el último invento de Andrew: ila Caja Knockout!

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: No One Can Hear You
description: Where are the citizens of Ooo?

title: Ya Nos Hackearon
description: Dendy ayuda a K.O., Enid y Rad a arreglar un problema técnico que amenaza con apoderarse de la bodega.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Panthro Plagiarized!
description: Vultureman has got a brand new invention but there's one big problem: he stole the idea from Panthro! Oh, also Vultureman is using his invention to take over Third Earth. So, there are two big problems.

title: Duncan Carving
description: Duncan takes advantage of a questionable Halloween legend to steal candy from his classmates.

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: The Heart
description: When Mr. Robinson accidentally let slip how little he cares for Gumball and Darwin, they react by giving him the cold shoulder.  Surprisingly Mr. Robinson misses them and tries to win back their friendship. After a few failed attempts, Gumball and Darwin realize that Mr. Robinson's heart is protecting him, so they give it an intense affection overload.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Escapism
description: Steven uses his psychic powers to find help.

title: La Cucarachita
description: Cuando la amada cucaracha mascota de Vic muere, Vic recurre a la magia oscura de Charlene para devolverle la vida.

title: Feria de ciencias misteriosas 201x
description: K.O. ayuda a Dendy con su proyecto para feria de ciencias.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Campista Profuga
description: Una fugitiva de un campamento de verano termina en el Tronco, pero Craig sospecha que su historia puede no ser lo que parece.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: ThunderSlobs
description: Tygra's feeling unappreciated by the other ThunderCats so he starts hanging out with Mumm-Ra and cleaning his Black Pyramid?! Whaaaaaaat?

title: Trick or Threat
description: Four kids in Justice League costumes are trick or treating on Halloween when they investigate a spooky house. As dangers befalls them inside, they come to realize that maybe they're not kids at all, but real Justice Leaguers under a spell.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Thomas' Promise
description: When Thomas and Diesel both want to deliver the same load to Whiff's Recycling Plant, Thomas suggests they each take half of the load, but Diesel turns it into a race.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Grown Up Stuff
description: Puppycorn doesn't want to grow up. To ease his woes, Unikitty spends the day teaching him all the fun things about being an adult.

title: El Hechicero Calavera
description: Separado de los demás, Cole debe encontrar su camino a la superficie para advertir al Rey Vangelis sobre el peligroso Hechicero Calavera.

title: Memory Mayhem
description: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

title: Fireworks
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Warrior Maiden Invasion
description: Third Earth is being overrun by super tough, super buff Warrior Maidens and it looks like the ThunderCats are next on their hit list! It's gonna be up to the ThunderKittens to save the day even though the kittens are so small and the Warrior Maidens are so big.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Beware the Scare-Crow
description: During a visit to the farm of Penny Bennyson's grandfather, Team Tennyson is constantly haunted by a Scare-Crow that's come to life, but when Ben discovers that Aristocrow is behind it all, our hero must defeat Aristocrow's master, the steam-powered Steam Smythe, if he is to save his cousin's farm!

title: Just Another Manic Mojo/Mime for a Change
description: Just Another Manic Mojo: The Powerpuff Girls lose their baseball in Mojo's house, offering him the perfect opportunity to destroy these pesky superheroines if he can only get them to sit still./Mime for a Change: An accidental bleach spill turns Rainbow the Clown into the malevolent Mr. Mime. He proceeds to turn Townsville black and white and dead all over.

title: Nom Nom's Entourage
description: Nom Nom recruits the Bears to act as his entourage of friends. But when the Bears realize Nom Nom doesn't understand friendship, they decide to kick their day of bonding into high gear.

title: Unlock the Magic: The Beginning
description: The discovery of an ancient, lost gateway leads the Care Bears on a rescue mission in the Silver Lining, a realm of natural wonders and comical creatures in the clouds beyond the borders of Care-A-Lot. While there, new discoveries expand the mission, challenging Cheer, Grumpy, and the mission team to grow beyond their present abilities and help the denizens of the Silver Lining.

title: The Question
description: Steven shows some city slicker gems how the cowboys lived.

title: The Origins Part 2
description: Via the sewers, Darwin finds himself flushed out to sea. He is terrified but determined to make his way back to the Wattersons. However, a fish can't get very far on land so Darwin will have to do millions of years of evolution in a matter of hours if he's going to get home safe and sound.

title: El Lider Del Ring
description: Cuando Ben tiene una racha ganadora en un videojuego, se le ocurre una idea para ganar un partido real de lucha, hasta que un luchador intimidante decide convertirlo en un verdadero desafío.

title: Trouble Busters!/French Fry Wars
description: Trouble Busters!: Now that the Awesome Brawlers are world famous Bakugan experts, they want to help people solve their Bakugan-related problems. When the world's quietest town is experiencing unexplained noises, the Awseome Brawlers are called in to get to the bottom of it./French Fry Wars: The Awesome Brawlers are arguing over who gets to eat the last french-fry. At first, each member makes a case for why they should to be the one to eat it. But the quarrel quickly escalates into trash talk and revealing secrets about one another. With everyone now upset, things take an unexpected turn.

title: Ener-G-Shoes
description: When Vic uses trickery to buy a pair of super cool sneakers from Maria Teresa's yard sale, the shoes try to walk him to his demise as punishment.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing 2
description: Charlie tells some scary stories featuring the Bears and their friends.

title: The Filth
description: Ben is tasked with cleaning the Rust Bucket. But when he is tricked into letting the villainous and vile Fly Guys steal it, he must chase them down before they create an unstoppable maggot monster with sights firmly set on destroying Las Vegas.

title: A Tall Tale
description: After Owen's BBF, Noah, goes through a growth spurt, Owen fears losing his friend and takes drastic action.

title: The Horror of Hook Mountain
description: Tygra takes Lion-O climbing up the peak of Hook Mountain to teach him a lesson about trust. But when they get trapped by a snowstorm and take refuge in a creepy cabin owned by the creepy Snowman - it's Tygra's ability to the trust that's gonna be tested.

title: Midnight at the Mayor's Mansion
description: When the Mayor's mansion is stalked by a vicious, ghostly monster, he calls the Powerpuff Girls for help.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: The Song of Mystery
description: A hideous creature named Que Horrifico is turning the children of Crystal Cove in to monsters. The adults in the town are in shock, reacting in the only way they know how, by abandoning their children and running away like cowards. Only Scooby and the gang stay behind to solve the mystery. Going undercover as a family - "Dad" Fred, "Mom" Daphne, "Grandma" Velma, "Son" Shaggy and "Baby" Scooby - the gang rents a house in order to capture Que Horrifico. But when their plan backfires and Que Horrifico uses his power over the monster children to cause them to attack the gang, it looks like all is lost. That is until a cartoon character named Broccoli Head comes to their rescue.

title: #AmigasDelAlma Parte 2
description: En este episodio especial de dos partes, las chicas deben rastrear a Katana, una guerrera misteriosa que está robando las almas de los villanos de Metrópolis. Mientras tanto, Tatsu, la nueva amiga de Diana, es su alma gemela en todo sentido, ipero puede que tenga una conexión con Katana!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: El Espantoso Segundo Especial de Halloween de Charlie
description: Charlie cuenta algunas historias de miedo protagonizadas por los Osos y sus amigos.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Too Hot to Handle
description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat so Lucas and his friends do whatever it takes to keep him from burning his mouth.

title: Reunited
description: Steven brings everyone together for a special reunion.

title: La Cucarachita
description: When Vic's beloved pet cockroach dies, Vic turns to Charlene's dark magic to bring her back to life.

title: The Vegging
description: Gumball and Darwin want to have a lazy day on the sofa, and have come up with various tricks to stop themselves having to move. Gradually more and more people arrive, seemingly to get them to move, until finally they realize that if they have to move, they'll do it in the laziest way possible.

title: Los Gatos Rascadores
description: Axel y el equipo deben ejecutar el control de daños después de que una chispa suelta de Minergy accidentalmente convierta los viejos juguetes de Zoe, un conjunto de lindos gatitos blandos, en una manada de bestias gruñendo.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Poodle Justice
description: It's Scooby's dream come true as the gang visits the set of his favorite TV show and he meets the star, his celebrity crush, a dog actress who plays a detective on the screen. Now all Scooby has to do is work up the courage to actually talk to her while also solving the mystery of the monstrous gargoyle attacking the production!

title: La Reina de los Munces
description: Jay, Nya y Lloyd son guiados entre las minas de Shintaro por Murt, quien los lleva de vuelta a la Cueva de los Munces. A la Reina Munce le gusta Jay.

title: La noche de fiesta de los villanos
description: Lord Box-man entra a la fuerza en una fiesta exclusiva para villanos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: We Got Hacked
description: Dendy helps KO, Enid and Rad stop a glitch that threatens to take over the bodega.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Mine Your Own Business
description: The gang explores a mining town and investigate a phantom miner, who's driving the business away from a nearby dude ranch.

title: Yogi's Tummy Troubles
description: Cindy puts a nuclear stomach in Yogi and he becomes an unstoppable eating machine.

title: The Real Fall!
description: An entire episode chronicles the ninja's most bizarre adventure yet: in which Cole, Princess Vania and Master Wu fall down a seemingly endless tunnel, into the bowels of Shintaro Mountain.

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: Juicio de Mino
description: Un grupo de Geckles creen que Kai y Zane están aliados con el Hechicero Calavera y los llevan con su líder, quien los somete a un juicio por Mino…

title: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call/Phantom Thief Ajit
description: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call: An archeological discovery is made in Los Volmos. Exploration at the site is cut short, when a master thief and his apprentice attempt to steal the ancient Bakugan artifacts. When the Awesome Brawlers hear the news, they step in to thwart the thieves./Phantom Thief Ajit: An Ancient Bakugon artifact from an archeological discovery is placed in the Los Volmos Museum. The Awesome Brawlers are charged with guarding the artifacts from any further attempts thievery.

title: Hare Restoration/TNT Trouble/Plumbers Quack
description: A self-interested Bugs gives Elmer Fudd dating advice. Wile E. Coyote runs into some dynamite problems. Elmer's leaky sink is no match for Daffy.

title: Monster Party
description: Enid is faced with a choice when her old friends from Ghoul School show up.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing
description: Charlie hosts an evening of spooky stories starring the Bears.

title: Beware the Beast from Below
description: Crystal Cove may be the most haunted town in the world but that doesn't stop Scooby and the gang from trying to prove that most of its most famous tourist attractions were fakes, much to the anger and dwindling profits of their parents. But when a radioactive barrel is accidentally opened releasing a hideous sewer beast that cocoons its victims in frozen yogurt, their mystery-solving skills are put to the test. After all, what could a sewer beast, a delicious edible dessert, underground caves and shrimping boats made of balloons possibly have in common? I'll give you a little hint - the local bank.

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: Knockout
description: Axel and the team juggle not waking Uncle Andrew from his nap and stopping Orangutank from stealing Andrew's latest invention: the Knockout Box!

title: Decoy for a Dognapper
description: Scooby impersonates a prize-winning Great Dane to catch whoever is stealing show dogs.

title: La pregunta
description: Steven les muestra a unas gemas citadinas cómo vivían los vaqueros.

title: King of the Zombeez
description: Frostferatu hires the Warriors to rid his castle of Zombeez when Neddy and a power mad zombie-bee queen take over.

title: Thomas Blasts Off
description: It's rocket launch day and all the trains get to help deliver the big rocket parts, but when Thomas is assigned a tiny part, he puts it off to help the others with their more exciting parts, not realizing that his "small" task was just as important.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Subway
description: The Bears are stranded on a subway platform after missing their train. But while waiting, the Bears are challenged with recovering some lost items.

title: #AcceptNoSubstitute
description: Feeling smothered, Babs urges her retired dad, Commissioner Gordon, to get a hobby, but her advice backfires when the Commissioner becomes a substitute teacher at her school!

title: Escapismo
description: Steven usa sus poderes psíquicos para conseguir ayuda.

title: Stakes Part 3: Vamps About
description: Five foes from Marceline's past come back to cause trouble for the Land of Ooo.

title: No Me Impresiona
description: Cuando un Corazoncito no se siente impresionado con las hazañas del departamento del sheriff, nuestros tres héroes intentan de todo para conquistarlo.

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Phased and Confused
description: When members of the Justice League are affected by the Phantom Zone ray and become phantom-like, their only hope for freedom is to somehow get a message to Booster Gold.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: El terror en la Montana Hook
description: Tigro lleva a León-O a la cima de la Montaña Hook para enseñarle una lección sobre la confianza. Pero cuando quedan atrapados por una tormenta de nieve y se refugian en una espeluznante cabaña propiedad del espeluznante Snowman, lo que se pondrá a prueba es la capacidad de Tigro para confiar.

title: Spooky Boo
description: After Clarence leads a few neighborhood kids through his homemade haunted house, Chelsea suggests they go to the high school kids haunted house for some real scares. When the gang makes a wrong turn they find themselves in a mysterious house on a hill full of creepy sounds, ghoulish shadows and mutant rat men!

title: The Creeping Creatures
description: A long time ago, there was a town called Gatorburg, where gators flowed wild and free and people got rich. Now, it's a ghost town. Gators are all dried up. But when Scooby and the gang receive an imitation Gatorburg purse, they decide to see for themselves if the gators really are gone. Forced to stay overnight when someone steals the engine to the Mystery Machine, they soon discover that gators have indeed returned - only these have comb-overs, walk on two legs and don't like visitors.

title: Umbrella, Umbrella
description: Pocoyo finds an umbrella. He and his friends have great fun playing with the umbrella and trying to work out what it's for. When it starts to rain, Pocoyo - with the help of the children watching - realizes a perfect use for it!

title: The Last Donnycorn
description: When Donny the Unicorn is hunted by a seemingly unstoppable foe, the Powerpuff Girls have to find a way to save him before it's too late!

title: Terror Tales of the Park
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Crisis en la roca de Ancianos
description: Una tragedia azota al Arroyo cuando los Ancianos quedan atrapados bajo la Roca Anciana. Ahora Craig, Kelsey y JP deben rescatarlos.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Revenge of the Man Crab
description: While hosting a volleyball tournament for Trickell's Triquid diet moisture, a smooth drinking beverage just like water except not so fatty, Crystal Cove beach finds itself attacked by a hideous man crab, who has taken a liking to the tournament's female players. Desperate to stop this beast before it scares away all the tourists, the gang investigates convinced it is a disgruntled local named Skipper Shelton, famous for his delicious clam filled waffle cones, his missing nose and his hatred for Crystal Cove bureaucrats. But when Daphne is captured by the Man Crab, Scooby and the gang have to put the mystery solving into overdrive or risk losing not only Daphne but the sanity of their leader Fred, who is not taking the abduction well.

title: Escape from Beyond the Cosmic
description: When Clarence accidentally breaks a local arcade game Jeff has become obsessed with, Clarence puts together his own real-life version of the game at home, encouraging Jeff to act out his fantasy in levels created exclusively by Clarence.

title: Game of Chicken
description: Fred gets a call for help from Chuck, his daredevil of a best friend, leading the gang on a rescue mission deep in the caverns of an ancient civilization. Once there, they learn of the real mystery: the ghost of the Tribal Warrior still protects the cavern from outsiders!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: A Nightmare on Aberdale Street: Balance's Revenge
description: In this Halloween adventure, Clarence uses a special jack-o-lantern to enter the world of people's dreams. He discovers that something mysterious is causing his friends to have nightmares, and Clarence needs to stop it!

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Camper on the Run
description: A runaway from a summer camp ends up at the Stump, but Craig suspects her story may not be what it seems.

title: Dungeon Party
description: Having survived their fall into the mountain, Cole, Wu and Princess Vania befriend a motley group of survivors, called the Lowly, and are told the story of how they too ended up at "Rock-Bottom."

title: Mermove Out
description: Seth is having a hard time sharing a room with messy Pascal and needs a change. But instead of being honest about the situation, Seth makes Pascal a mermaid tail so that his brother can finally move out - into the ocean!

title: Kelsey the Worthy
description: When Kelsey demolishes a wall at Craig's house, her father takes away her sword. So she enlists Craig and JP to help prove to her father that she's still worthy.

title: Charmed, I'm Sure
description: Still stranded on the monster planet Anur Transyl, Ben and Rook reluctantly team up with Charmcaster to take on Zs' Skayr.

title: A Mystery Solving Gang Divided!
description: Scooby-Doo and the gang travel to Chambersburg, a battlefield near Gettysburg, to investigate the mysterious appearance of ghost zombie Civil War soldiers and come face to face with a rival mystery solving gang, the Funky Phantom crew. The rivalry between the two gangs gets so out of hand that it threatens to keep either group from solving the mystery, until the ghost of Abraham Lincoln appears and tries to get them focused.

title: Terror Tales of the Park V
description: The fifth installment of Terror Tales finds Benson trying to spice up the park's annual Halloween party by renting a wish making machine.

title: La noche de los villanos en casa
description: Mientras Box-man y Venomous no están, Darrell y Shannon cuidan a Fink, aunque él no quiera.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Pantro robado
description: Buitro tiene un nuevo invento, pero hay un gran problema: ile robó la idea a Pantro! Ah, y además Buitro usa su invento para apoderarse del Tercer Planeta. De modo que hay dos grandes problemas.

title: El metro
description: Luego de perder el tren, los Osos quedan varados en una plataforma del subterráneo. Pero mientras esperan, se desafían a recuperar algunos objetos perdidos.

title: Taz in Toyland
description: After Taz breaks all of his toys, Granny gives him one last chance to care for something.

title: Octi Evil/Geshundfight
description: Octi Evil: The heinous Him toys with Bubbles' mind by speaking to her through Octi, her favorite stuffed animal. Following Him's orders, Bubbles picks a fight with her sisters that lands them all in a time-out./Geshundfight: The Amoeba Boys' ill-conceived plan to stand in Townsville Park all night in the rain leaves them with a nasty virus that's really something to sneeze at.

title: Mystery Science Fair 201X
description: KO helps Dendy with her science fair project.

title: Baku-Gear/Bakugan Rock!
description: Baku-Gear: The Awesome Brawlers are excited over their discovery of Baku-Gear, and want to get some footage of it in action. While they're filming, an underclassman named Trey challenges Dan to battle. Who will emerge victorious in the impromptu battle?/Bakugan Rock!: Baku-gear has shown up twice for Dan and Drago and it's starting to eat away at the other awesome brawlers. It's time they take it into their own hands. When Lia and Wynton go up against the rockin' new brawlers in town, they show Dan and Drago that they are not the only one who can summon this cool new tool!

title: Rad Monster Party
description: Ben and Rook enlist the help of intergalactic smuggler Rad Dudesman to fly them through the Anur System, the home of the monstrous aliens!

title: Lords of Ghost Town
description: When V&V recruit a ghost to scare away a bully, they end up messing with the realm of the dead, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: La traicion
description: Tigro se siente poco apreciado por los demás Thundercats...i¿y por eso empieza a pasar tiempo con Mumm-Ra y a limpiar su Pirámide Negra?!

title: Blank Eyed Girl
description: One very spooky night, Finn and Jake come face-to-face with an urban myth.

title: Terror Tales of the Park IV
description: The park guys try to keep Muscle Man awake with scary stories on a long drive so that they can meet his mom.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Tercera parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 3 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Bewitched, Bothered and Bothered Some More!
description: Flonk hires the Warriors to make Witch Way change his brother Helmut from a frog back to human.

title: Not Impressed
description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

title: Ren Faire
description: Clarence and his pals venture to the Aberdale Renaissance Faire. Clarence confuses a medieval play for reality, and vows to stop the evil black knight from getting the princess.

title: What a Night for a Knight
description: Scooby-Doo and Shaggy stumble across a lone suit of black armor and embark on a quest to find the artifact's missing owner.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Squashening
description: To escape a monster, the girls have to tell him a scary story.

title: Gorilla in Our Midst
description: Grape Ape crashes in the middle of town, turning Jellystone into a disaster zone! The citizens must band together to move this mountain of a monkey.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: All Trick No Treat
description: On Halloween, Axel gets too caught up in the scares and loses track of the fun - just in time for an infiltration by the worst trick 'r' treater of all, Madcap!

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Grand Scam
description: Shaggy takes the Gang to the Minor League Baseball stadium of his youth only to learn that it's about to be shut down because a Ghostly Baseball Player is scaring away the fans and the team! Shaggy puts aside his cowardly ways to saves his home team but will Scooby stand by his, now not so scared, pal?

title: Villains' Night In
description: While Boxman and Venomous are out, Fink is reluctantly babysat by Darrell and Shannon.

title: Fun Proof
description: Apple and Onion want to become this week's "Most Fun People".

title: Pequena graduacion
description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

title: Flirty Phantom
description: Lost in Transylberia, the Warriors come to a haunted house for help and meet a young ghost lady inside that wants to spend the rest of her afterlife with Prohyas!

title: Hassle in the Castle
description: The sleuths shipwreck on a deserted island and explore a haunted castle.

title: Crisis at Elder Rock
description: Tragedy strikes the Creek when the Elders get trapped under Elder Rock, and it's up to Craig, Kelsey and JP to rescue them.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Terror Tales of the Park II
description: The park can be a very scary place at night.

title: Lost Sword
description: Lion-O is reminded that he needs to plug the Sword of Omens into the Cats' Lair each night or else the base will run out of power. That's fine, it's not like Lion-O's going to accidentally lose the sword or anything. Right?

title: Witch's Crew
description: On Halloween Night, Morbucks summons a monster that she didn't expect.

title: Ghoul Spirit
description: Gwen rejects the friendship of a friendly ghost.

title: The Rooters of All Evil
description: Meet the Rooters, the Black Ops wing of the Plumbers from the Null Void. They've come looking for someone close to Ben, and they mean business!

title: The Ring Leader
description: While winning big on a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben gets the idea to win a wrestling match for real until an intimidating wrestler named Iron Kyle decides to make it a true challenge.

title: Terror Tales of the Park III
description: Each of the park guys want to win a bet by telling the scariest story at a Halloween party.

title: El Huesped
description: iVic y Val se culpan el uno al otro por comer toda la comida de la cocina y hacer un gran lío! Pero pronto descubren que la culpa es de un fantasma. iAhora deben pedir la ayuda de Achi para librar al mundo de los espíritus que hay a su alrededor y echar al fantasma de su casa!

title: Under a Red Sun
description: Steppenwolf "boom tubes" Superman to a planet with a red sun in order to make the Man of Steel powerless. Somehow Batman and Big Barda have to locate the planet before Superman is destroyed.

title: Overdue Duck/Hole Gag: Bees/Vincent Van Fudd
description: At the library, Porky Pig tries to silence a troublemaking Daffy Duck. Bugs Bunny interrupts Elmer Fudd's attempt to be a great artist.

title: Escuela De Payasos
description: Mientras Ben disfruta en el estacionamiento a la salida de un partido de fútbol americano de ex estudiantes de la Universidad de State, se alía con los antiguos compañeros del Abuelo Max para impedir que Zombozo, un payaso demente, le robe a todo el público durante el entretiempo.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: 15 Minutes of Fame
description: When Bubbles' video goes viral, she goes to great lengths to maintain her status as a big-time director.

title: Reunificados
description: Steven reúne a todos para un evento especial.

title: Gnome More Mister Nice Guy
description: When the daycare gets taken over by evil gnomes, Duncan finds himself on the wrong team.

title: The Big Squeak
description: Avocado's new toy is driving everyone crazy with its noisy squeaker. Lucas tells everyone that he's going to speak to her and realizes Avocado loves everything about her squeaky toy apart from the actual squeak itself! So, Dr. Lucas is in the house to operate and remove the squeak.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: La invasion de las guerreras amazonas
description: El Tercer Planeta está siendo invadido por Guerreras Amazonas con fuerza y músculos extraordinarios iy parece que los Thundercats son los siguientes en su lista de ataques! Ahora, la seguridad de todos dependerá de los Thundercachorros, aunque sean tan pequeños y las Guerreras Amazonas sean tan grandes.

title: Ghostfreaked Out
description: Ben's internal demons get externalized when Ghostfreak escapes from his watch and becomes a full fledged being on his own. The renegade alien then realizes he needs to meld with Ben's DNA in order to survive.

title: What a Night for a Dark Knight!
description: When Scooby and the gang come to Gotham City to visit Alfred Pennyworth, they stumble into a dangerous mystery! Alfred's been kidnapped by the Man-Bat! Batman is on the case and he does not want any help from our meddling kids.

title: Blukic and Driba Go to Area 51
description: A mysterious Galvan arrives and demands Blukic and Driba to give back a super powerful weapon needed to stop a threat to Earth.

title: La Venganza de Bao Bao
description: Cuando el antiguo compañero de Mao Mao amenaza al reino, los amigos de Mao Mao tendrán que conocer su pasado para proteger el presente.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: La Gran Caida
description: Este episodio relata cómo Cole, la princesa Vania y el maestro Wu caen por un túnel aparentemente interminable, dentro de la montaña de Shintaro.

title: EEBows
description: Tired of getting pinched, the Titans' elbows rebel and soon bend the very fabric of time and space.

title: Prickly Pair
description: After leaving Little Homeschool, Steven has found a new hobby, plants.

title: Los Vegetales
description: Gumball y Darwin solo quieren holgazanear todo el día, pero terminan teniendo que salvar al resto de la familia.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Afraid of the Dark
description: When UG helps a little girl who is afraid of the dark, he convinces her there's nothing to be afraid of but their imaginations.  But when their imaginations prove to be pretty terrifying, they go on a quest to turn on the lights.

title: Scary Tales
description: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! To get him in the holiday spirit, the gang tell their own ideas of what a spooky story is, hoping to scare the emotionless Rick for once, with each tale even scarier (and sillier) than the last!

title: Brawler Headhunting/Lightning's Entrance Exam
description: Brawler Headhunting: As acting president of Kazami International, Shun is called upon to entertain another new young CEO Luca Schmidt, who's interested in doing business with the Kazami International. But Shun quickly realizes something is up when Luca tries woo him over to his brawling team - the Glanz Five. /Lightning's Entrance Exam: The Awesome Brawlers may be world famous heroes, but that doesn't mean they get out of going to school. They are still regular kids, doing regular kid things. But teachers may have something to say when Lightening decides he wants to join his buddies in the classroom.

title: Familiar
description: Con tantos cambios en su vida, Steven intenta encontrar su lugar en el mundo.

title: The Mysterious Boy/A New Power
description: The Mysterious Boy: After stopping Tiko's rampage, the Awesome Brawlers have become world-famous heroes and Bakugan-mania sweeps the globe. With the Bakugan boom, brawling has been reinvented as a sporting game. In celebration of the Awesome Brawlers efforts, a tournament is being held in their honor. But the battles are quickly cut short when a rogue brawler and his golden Bakugan crash the event./A New Power: A Rogue brawler, Agit and his golden Bakugan have crashed the Awesome Brawlers party. Who is this brawler? How can he control a Golden Bakugan? Only one way to find out - Bakugan Brawl! Dan and Drago go head to head with the outsides to get to the bottom of it. Outmatched by their opponent, Dan and Drago get a little help from a new powerful weapon - Baku-Gear.

title: Whale Spotting
description: Apple and Onion need to join an exclusive club to see a rare whale.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Reunion en la Oscuridad
description: Axel debe ayudar a Bearbarian a superar su miedo secreto a la oscuridad para evitar que Dynamo le robe su viaje.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Peebles' Pet Shop of Terrible Terrors!
description: Scooby and the Mystery Inc. gang meet Wanda Sykes, who is helping save a bunch of cute, fuzzy animals up for adoption in a large pet supply store. When a crazy monster egg hatches a monster in the pet store's back room, our heroes and Wanda must not only save the store and the animals, but their own lives!

title: Bye Bye
description: Meet Bing and his friends… Join us and celebrate the noisy, joyful, messy reality of preschool life.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Gathering Dark
description: Axel must help Bearbarian overcome his secret fear of the dark to stop Dynamo from stealing his ride.

title: Stakes Part 4: Empress Eyes
description: When one of her oldest adversaries targets the Ice Kingdom, Marceline rushes to Simon's rescue.

title: Sal's Our Pal
description: When Victor and Valentino learn Tez has appointed himself the town leader "Huey Tlatoani" of Monte Macabre, they set out to un-seat him with the help of everyone's pal, Sal.

title: Belson's Sleepover
description: Belson invites Clarence and friends to a sleepover party, with a catch: whoever can survive the night's pranks and scares will win Belson's old Acedia game system!

title: Gyranoid of the Future
description: Apple and Onion struggle to ride Gyranoid of the Future, the craziest roller coaster at the carnival.

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Trial By Mino
description: Separated from the others, Kai and Zane discover a party of Geckles who suspect them of being in league with the Skull Sorcerer, and bring them before their leader, Chancellor Gulch, who subjects them to a "Trial-By-Mino."

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Get the Egg Home
description: When an egg blows down into the village, it is Mush-Mush and friends' mission to return it to Mush Mountain. Two problems though: there is a Beetle Boom on and all the beetles try to charge and knock over Mushables, and Lilit has always wanted to see an egg hatch so secretly drags her feet.

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Scared Silly
description: When the Rust Bucket runs out of gas on a foggy East Coast road, Ben, Gwen and Max are forced to stay at a hotel being menaced by Creepy Carl, a local folklore expert, who may actually be a ghost!

title: Equipo Monstruo
description: Los Titanes quieren convertirse en los mejores del pueblo a la hora de pedir dulces o trucos en Halloween y, para ello, Raven lanza un hechizo que los convierte en monstruos reales.

title: Energy Shoes
description: Cuando Vic usa engaños para comprar un par de zapatillas espectaculares de la venta de garaje de María Teresa, el calzado trata de llevarlo a su perdición como castigo.

title: Las historias de Halloween de Charlie
description: Charlie es el presentador de unas historias de terror protagonizadas por los Osos.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Segunda parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 2 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Bao Bao's Revenge
description: When Mao Mao's old partner threatens the kingdom, his friends will need to learn about his past in order to protect the present.

title: Various Modes of Transportation
description: With the other Titans away, Cyborg is forced to take a road trip with Robin.

title: The Return
description: Ghostfreak has returned! And he has brought a Mummy, Werewolf and Frankenstein like aliens with him to help him shroud the Earth in darkness.

title: Developing Dilemna
description: Frankie lets Elliott get a pet, which doesn't go down well with their new neighbor.

title: Trick or Creek
description: It's Halloween at the Creek, and Craig is on a mission to collect as much candy as humanly possible, but a spooky ghoul from the Creek's past threatens his haul.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Drum Roll Please
description: Pocoyo and his playmates love dancing to the Ball Orchestra's music. When it stops, they try to make their own band. Sleepy Bird's snoring sets the rhythm, and together they all make a wonderful, harmonious din.

title: Uh, Oh, Dynamo
description: Worried about his little girls' safety, the Professor creates Powerpuff Dynamo, a state-of-the-art protection system, to help them in battle.

title: Spoooooky Game
description: The gang's weekly board game night has been getting a little too competitive lately, so when Unikitty finds a spooky old board game that's clearly haunted, their desire to win gets turned upside down, but cursed or not, they'll be the first to the finish line!

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Yard Sale
description: Each of the Bears get offbeat items at a local yard sale. Their new possessions send them on their own separate adventures.

title: Pruebas de Diversion
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren convertirse en la "Gente más divertida" de esta semana.

title: Boogie Frights/Abracadaver
description: Boogie Frights: The Boogie Man creates perpetual night by launching a huge disco ball to block out the sun. While evil creatures are dancing and destroying in the dark, the Powerpuff Girls plot to crash the ball./Abracadaver: Al Lusion, the old-time Townsville magician, pulls off his greatest stunt yet when he comes back from the dead as the zombie Abracadaver to haunt Townsville.
